(**
# Reporting Issues #

MordhauBuddy logs runtime data to text files that are cleaned up as they 
grow stale or become too numerous to keep file sizes low. Please include 
this data as necessary when reporting [issues](https://github.com/Shmew/MordhauBuddy/issues).

If you encounter any issues while using this application you can navigate 
to the following locations:

 - Windows
   - `C:\Users\<user>\AppData\Local\mordhau-buddy-updater\logging`
 - Linux
   - `~/.local/share/mordhau-buddy/logging`

*)
